

# Local secrets - never commit any of these
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.p12
*_secret*
*_token*
# Whitelist: legitimate security tooling, not actual secrets
!deskad_keyboard_demo/tools/scan_secrets.py
.netrc
.npmrc

# Editor / backup leftovers that might contain old secrets
*.bak
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Python/runtime noise
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.log
.pytest_cache/

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/

# Generated uploads/artifacts
*/static/uploads/
*/static/posters/
deskad_keyboard_demo/static/models/desk_setup_*.glb
deskad_keyboard_demo/static/models/keyboard_*.glb
deskad_keyboard_demo/static/models/uploaded_*.glb
deskad_keyboard_demo/training/output/
deskad_keyboard_demo/training/datasets/

# Runtime job stores / quality reports
deskad_keyboard_demo/data/runtime/

# 작업일지/인수인계/실험리포트/CAD 레퍼런스 — 전용 폴더, 로컬 전용 (GitHub 비공개)
deskad_keyboard_demo/worklogs/

# docs/ 는 공식문서(사용설명서·보고서·가이드)만 공개한다 — 기본 무시 후 공식문서만 화이트리스트.
# 새 작업일지를 docs/에 떨궈도 자동으로 비공개; 공식문서는 아래에 한 줄씩 추가해 공개한다.
deskad_keyboard_demo/docs/*
!deskad_keyboard_demo/docs/deploy.md
!deskad_keyboard_demo/docs/security.md
!deskad_keyboard_demo/docs/architecture.md
!deskad_keyboard_demo/docs/schema.md

# Large local model artifacts
models/
*.safetensors
*.ckpt
*.pt
*.pth
*.gguf
